  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "5971e1b2",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "In this notebook we will try to recreate the analyses: \n",
    "\n",
    "[ABaCo demo: Parkinson's disease gut microbiome](https://mona-abaco.readthedocs.io/en/latest/tutorial/demo-parkinson.html)\n",
    "\n",
    "> _This notebook is used as a demo of ABaCo's capabilities on integrating multiple studies with multiple biomes. In this case, the Parkinson's dataset contains samples from the gut microbiome from 5 different studies._\n",
    "\n",
    "but starting from mgnipy to get taxa tables and metadata"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "id": "1b614ce6",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "from mgnipy import MGnipy\n",
    "import asyncio "
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 3,
   "id": "dc9452c2",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "name": "stderr",
